---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | John Doe">
  <main class="py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Me</h1>
    
    <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-lg mb-6">
        Hi! I'm John Doe, a software developer and food enthusiast who combines my passion for technology with my love for exploring world cuisines, especially noodles.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">My Journey</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        With over 5 years of experience in full-stack development, I've worked with startups and established companies alike. My technical expertise includes JavaScript/TypeScript, React, Node.js, and Python. Currently, I work remotely, which allows me to pursue my other passion: traveling the world and discovering unique food experiences.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">What I Do</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Develop web applications using modern technologies</li>
        <li>Write about my travel and food experiences</li>
        <li>Create content about developer lifestyle and remote work</li>
        <li>Contribute to open-source projects</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Current Focus</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        I'm currently focused on building tools that help digital nomads and remote workers find the best places to work and eat around the world. When I'm not coding, you can find me exploring local food markets or trying out new recipes in my temporary kitchen.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Get in Touch</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        I'm always interested in connecting with fellow developers and food enthusiasts. Feel free to reach out to me on social media or via email.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex gap-4 mt-8">
        <a 
          href="mailto:hello@johndoe.com"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700"
        >
          Email Me
        </a>
        <a 
          href="/resume"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-purple-600 text-base font-medium rounded-md text-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-50 dark:hover:bg-purple-900"
        >
          View Resume
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
